== <Big><div style="text-shadow: 0 0 0.2em grey, 0 0.1em 0.05em grey, 0 -0.1em 0.05em grey, 0.05em 0 0.05em grey, -0.05em 0 0.05em grey;padding: 15px;font-family: Montagu Slab, Serif;text-align: center;font-size: 30px">Entities</span></big> ==
{{Underline|aaaaaa}}
<Div style="border-left: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color);padding: 15px;border-right: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color);">
Although [[Level 135.1]] appears devoid of entities, reports confirm the presence of entities within the sublevel. Among the most consistently noted are the [[Entity 36|Lighters]], [[Entity 53|False Grass]], and [[Entity 55|Tornado Head]]. These beings are rarely encountered, usually obscured by the unstable visibility and the deceptive calmness of the surrounding.

